  <description><![CDATA[<p>Chia Laguna Resort is a perfect choice for both couples and families. With four hotels set within an expansive resort, you can be sure of a wonderful holiday with something for everyone. The resort sits at the foot of the mountains in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc3361d2d7a945d38852da5e20516d75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc3361d2d7a945d38852da5e20516d75}" title="Southern Sardinia">South Sardinia</a>, close to some of the most picturesque beaches on the island, where a seemingly-endless stretch of white sand leads to crystal-clear waters.</p>
<p>Those who want to stay active will appreciate the numerous activities on offer here, including sports courts and academies for football and dance, watersports and bicycles for rent. And when it’s time to relax there’s a fantastic spa with a large choice of treatments as well as several swimming pools. After a busy day, you’ll be spoilt for choice with nine restaurants offering delicious cuisine and bars including the champagne bar with views of the ocean.</p>
<p>Children are well-catered for with fun clubs for ages three up to 17. There’s also a nursery for babies and the resort offers amenities like prams, changing mats and baby baths for its youngest guests.</p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Chia Laguna Resort is approx. 1 hour from Cagliari airport.</p>]]></description>
